Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界我最喜欢你了
